The techno-organic mandrill came out of the compartment. He looked at 
the crashed Autobot ship.

Gesper: That ship of yours, it does not look like a warship... Can you 
tell me what your mission was in the first place? (He turn to Hoist) 
Good day! I am Gesper, Tripredacus ambassador, at least for now. What 
is your name?
